These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, juice, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, fishing, singing
1. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking fanta##7
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | juice | soy-milk       | milk | fanta        |
| Hobby      | fishing  | dancing | singing        | camping |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, hamster, fish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, weightlifting, swimming, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the owner of the hamster##7
2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hamster | lizard       | fish         | bird     |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | parkour | swimming | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, adventure, spy, horror
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, ambient, rock, metal
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of metal is somewhere between the fan of ambient and the fan of funk##7
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of metal and the person watching adventure movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror | spy | documentary  |
| Music-Genre   | rock | funk  | metal   | ambient |

