.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, card-games, cooking, singing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, baseball, handball, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's hobby is singing##7
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | card-games | rock-climbing | singing       | cooking |
| Sport   | baseball      | soccer   | handball | water-polo  |

