.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, puzzles, card-games, chess
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, spanish, colombian, french
1. the french is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
2. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the french is somewhere between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##7
5. the french is on the left of the colombian##1
6. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the french##5
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | card-games | filmmaking   | chess | puzzles |
| Nationality   | nigerian      | spanish | french      | colombian |

