.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, iced-tea, lemonade
There are 4 different nationalities: british, canadian, italian, colombian
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the italian##1
2. the italian is the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the canadian is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the colombian##3
6. the colombian is somewhere between the british and the canadian##7
7. the italian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee | juice      | iced-tea | lemonade     |
| Nationality   | british    | colombian | canadian   | italian |

