.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, kale, onion, cauliflower
There are 4 different nationalities: french, italian, dutch, german
1. the french is on the far left##1
2. the person eating kale is on the left of the italian##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left or far right##3
4. the german is somewhere between the person eating spinach and the person eating onion##7
5. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person eating onion##5
6. the german is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | cauliflower    | spinach   | kale | onion  |
| Nationality   | french | dutch | german    | italian |

