.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, chinese, canadian, thai
4 different pets are kept: frog, pony, mouse, bird
1. the chinese is not the owner of the bird##6
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
3. the thai is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the canadian is somewhere between the thai and the nigerian##7
5. the chinese is on the left of the nigerian##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | thai | canadian | chinese | nigerian |
| Pet           | mouse   | bird    | frog       | pony  |

