.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, designer, librarian, musician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, d&b, rock, metal
1. the firefighter is not the fan of jazz##6
2. the librarian is on the right of the firefighter##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
4. the firefighter is on the right of the fan of metal##1
5. the librarian is somewhere between the fan of metal and the designer##7
6. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the fan of rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | musician | firefighter | librarian | designer |
| Music-Genre   | metal         | rock      | jazz | d&b            |

