.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, comedy, zombie, drama
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, fish, turtle
1. the person watching drama movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the owner of the turtle##7
2. the person watching comedy movies is not the owner of the fish##6
3. the owner of the horse is not the person watching zombie movies##6
4. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
5. the person watching disaster movies is the owner of the cat##1
6. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | drama | comedy | zombie |
| Pet           | cat    | horse   | turtle  | fish      |

