.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, sports, zombie, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, classical, r&b, jazz
1. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the fan of classical is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person watching family movies is between the person watching sports movies and the fan of classical##2
6. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the fan of classical and the person watching sports movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | family | sports | zombie   |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | r&b      | country      | jazz |

