3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person who's hobby is video-games##6
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is hiking##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | hiking | dancing | camping | video-games |
| Sport   | snowboarding  | skateboarding    | rowing    | cricket  |

