2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | drawing | gardening | dancing | video-games |
| Transport   | helicopter   | train      | snowmobile        | jet-ski  |

