.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, lemonade, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, rock, punk, techno
1. the fan of rock is in an even position##4
2. the fan of techno is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the fan of punk##7
3. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
4. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the fan of punk##1
7. the person drinking milk is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | lemonade | milk | soy-milk   |
| Music-Genre   | country | punk   | techno | rock |

