The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, roller, skateboard, van
1. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the owner of the rabbit##7
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | rabbit    | mouse | frog     | turtle |
| Transport   | skateboard | van  | roller | tram |

 